fields.name: Noah: The REAL Story
fields.overview: You may know the story of Noah and the Ark from children's books or cartoons or even movies.  But have you ever read the story in the Bible?  You may be surprised by what's in there!

fields.name: God? Are you there?
fields.overview: Any person of faith has wondered from time to time whether their faith is justified. This activity addresses the question of whether God exists or not.
